{"body": "Thanks for the comments @jeremy - I've updated the code. Anything else?\n\nMy only thought is about whether:\n```ruby\nprefix + text[start_pos..end_pos].strip + postfix\n```\nshould be:\n```ruby\n\"#{prefix}#{text[start_pos..end_pos].strip}#{postfix}\"\n```\n(https://github.com/ihid/rails/blob/7e82ebd25eec470b57f8fba3aeafb597561091b6/actionpack/lib/action_view/helpers/text_helper.rb#L149)\n\nI think it's best left as it is, but it seems to be a similar situation to `\"#{count || 0} #{word}\"` so I thought it worth mentioning.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5797929", "created_at": "2012-05-18T23:44:20Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6384#issuecomment-5797929", "updated_at": "2012-05-18T23:44:20Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6384, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/iHiD", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/955103d80e386882143a78875fb727bf?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F66a04212026e6c48b31b7a1e06c1c597.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD/received_events", "gravatar_id": "955103d80e386882143a78875fb727bf", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "iHiD", "type": "User", "id": 286476, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iHiD/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e5d43bd354364b900f781"}, "id": 5797929, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6384"}
